  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic, ginger, cumin, and smoked paprika; cook 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add cottage cheese and stir to combine.",
    "Add soy sauce, red pepper flakes, and beef broth; bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, for 15 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in black pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Warm injera bread according to package instructions.",
    "Spoon cheese-pull over injera and serve immediately."
